Date: Wed, 18 Feb 2026 13:58:48 +0300
Subject: [PATCH 4/5] Feature: group-by-column in library tree
 (symbol/footprint chooser)

Add GROUP node type to LIB_TREE_MODEL for grouping library items by
any column value. Context menu on column header: 'Group by X' /
'Remove Grouping'. Persisted in app settings. Updated synchronizing
adapters for Symbol Editor and Footprint Editor.
